u.s. to ask japan to drop beef restrict u.s. agricultur secretari richard lyng will ask the japanes govern to remov all beef import restrict when he visit there next month . lyng 's remark came in a speech at oklahoma state univers today . `` we think japanes consum should have the same freedom of choic as our consum . look at all the japanes camera and tape record in thi room . we know they 'd buy more beef if they had the opportun , '' lyng said .